            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-112af7d90f46baad-58df80 twpub-112af7d90f46baad-25d4bc twpub-112af7d90f46baad-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><a></a><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/112af7d90f46baad/text/000000603\"><span class=\"label\">[28]</span></$link> P. 120. Damiens, who attempted the life of Louis XV. in 1757, was born at Arras, capital of Artois (AtrÃ©batie).</p></div></div>"
