            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-112af7d90f46baad-58df80 twpub-112af7d90f46baad-25d4bc twpub-112af7d90f46baad-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><a></a><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/112af7d90f46baad/text/000000619\"><span class=\"label\">[32]</span></$link> P. 123. Admiral Byng was shot on March 14, 1757.</p></div></div>"
