            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-112af7d90f46baad-58df80 twpub-112af7d90f46baad-25d4bc twpub-112af7d90f46baad-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"bbox\"><p>There are two instances of Massa Carara (<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/112af7d90f46baad/text/000000229\">pp. 43</$link> and <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/112af7d90f46baad/text/000000232\">45</$link>) and one instance of Massa-Carrara (<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/112af7d90f46baad/text/000000026\">page ix</$link>). As this latter is in the Introduction, i.e. distinct from the book proper, it has been retained.</p></div></div>"
